<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
<locus from="10v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2113OntheB" xml:lang="en">On the birth of our Lord of the blessed Virgin Mary</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#10v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ድርሳን፡ ዘርቱዐ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ በእንተ፡ ልደተ፡ አምላክ፡ እማርያም፡ እምቅድስት፡</incipit>
</msItem>


<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
<locus from="24v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2095OnHowO">On the baptism of our Lord</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#24v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ተጠምቀ፡ አምላክነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በፈለገ፡ ዮርዳኖስ፡ በዕደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
<locus from="40r"/>
<title>For the beginning of Lent </title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#40r" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ዘይትነበብ፡ በቀበላ፡ ጾም፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
<locus from="47r"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT6049SundayRetuaH">For the (first) Sunday of Lent </title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#47r" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ድርሳን፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በቅድስት፡ ጾም፡ ሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በእንተ፡ ጾም፡ እመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ምግባራት፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
<locus from="51r"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT6050SundayRetuaH">For the second Sunday of Lent </title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#51r" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ድርሳን፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በካዕብ፡ ሰንበተ፡ ጾም፡ በዕለተ፡ ቦአ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ምኵራበ፡ ወመሐረ፡ በእንተ፡ ጾም፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ እመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ምግባራት፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
<locus from="54r"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT6061SundayRetuaH">For the third Sunday of Lent </title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#54r" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ድርሳን፡ ዘሣልስ፡ ሰንበተ፡ ጾም፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በመጻጉዕ፡ በእንተ፡ ጾም፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ እመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ምግባራት፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
<locus from="57r"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT6045SerataSegdat">Services for the close of Lent</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#57r" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ሥርዓተ፡ ስግደት፡ በተፍጻሜተ፡ በዓለ፡ ቅድስት፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9">
<locus from="72v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2097OnHowt">On the incarnation of the Word</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#72v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>በከመ፡ ተሠገወ፡ ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወእማርያም፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
<locus from="88v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT6048OnPalmSundayRetuaH">For Palm Sunday</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#88v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ዘይትነበብ፡ በዕለተ፡ ሆሣዕና፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
<locus from="92v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2149OntheW">On our Lord washing the feet of his disciples, and on the Last Supper</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#92v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ሐፀበ፡ እግረ፡ አርዳኢሁ፡ ወዘከመ፡ ወሀበ፡ ኅብስተ፡ ወወይነ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ድራር፡ ለአርዳኢሁ፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
<locus from="109v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2118OntheD">On the death of our Lord</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#109v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>በእንተ፡ ሞቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ጊዜ፡ ፱ሰዓት፡ በዲበ፡ ዕፀ፡ መስቀል፡
ወበእንተ፡ ፈያታዊ፡ ዘየማን፡ ወበእንተ፡ ሞት፡ ወሰይጣን፡ ዘከመ፡ ተበሃሉ፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13">
<locus from="125r"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2109OntheA">On the ascension of our Lord</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez" xml:lang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#125r"></locus>ድርሳን፡ በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ዓርገ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማያት፡ መልዕልተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ስም፡ ወነበረ፡ በየማነ፡ ኃይል፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.14">
<locus from="132v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2137OntheP">On the Trinity in unity</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#132v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ርድአኒ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ከመ፡ እትናገር፡ በእንተ፡ ህሉና፡ መስልሥትከ፡ በተዋህዶትከ፡ </incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.15">
<locus from="148v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT6047On12ApostlesRetuaH">On the twelve apostles</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez">በእንተ፡ ፲ወ፪ሐዋርያት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ አመ፡ ፭ሐምሌ</textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#148v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ርድአኒ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ከመ፡ እትናገር፡ በእንተ፡ ህሉና፡ መስልሥትከ፡ በተዋህዶትከ፡ </incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.16">
<locus from="154r"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2145OntheT">On the transfiguration of our Lord</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#154r" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ድርሳን፡ ዘደብረ፡ ታቦር፡ ዘከመ፡ ተወለጠ፡ ራዕዩ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ በውስተ፡ ደብረ፡ ታቦር፡</incipit>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.17">
<locus from="160v"/>
<title type="complete" ref="LIT2124OntheF">On the four beasts</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
<incipit><locus target="#160v" xml:lang="gez"></locus>ድርሳን፡ ዘ፬እንስሳ፡ ክቡራን፡</incipit>
</msItem>

